{"tid":2396931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次仆街了 deloitte被爆大鑊","createTime":"2021-02-06T04:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T10:27:53.000Z","uid":40745,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5c90239ce7f9b5f386413cdb276886b683f16a","tid":2396931,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"雖然係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知邊個係今次最大贏家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本週三（3日）有一名德勤華永會計師事務所（特殊普通合夥）員工，將一份長達55頁的powerpoint文件傳送到公司郵件，舉報了4年工作期間各種不合規的人和事，當中有十宗爆料事件，本文抽取了當中三宗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/240617?fbclid=IwAR1CC6q2uwU3w191rGwjts7ZdQxiztegR3nbnix8bqrFI7Mf0WCmtMS5_cQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F240617%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1CC6q2uwU3w191rGwjts7ZdQxiztegR3nbnix8bqrFI7Mf0WCmtMS5_cQ&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=0a65e382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/240617?fbclid=IwAR1CC6q2uwU3w191rGwjts7ZdQxiztegR3nbnix8bqrFI7Mf0WCmtMS5_cQ</a><br />\n<br />\n該員工同時表示，「如今，德勤管理層和RRG的所作所為已經逾越了審計道德底線，而作為審計從業者中的一員，我有義務將我知道的一切真相公之於眾，作出我認為正確的決定。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rLy8By.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rLy8By.jpg&h=283aa23f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8W21Wy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8W21Wy.jpg&h=981e26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXK8c3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXK8c3e.jpg&h=d973b89f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TO5Z39U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTO5Z39U.jpg&h=fbefc264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3593e4a05fbd13cf40f35fcd0727d224e938247e","tid":2396931,"uid":4128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"<im